{"tid":2161173,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【深田えいみ】呢鋪GG了 深田えいみ「七味粉挑戰」玩大咗","createTime":"2020-08-17T11:57:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T12:45:16.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a45e3e6a548cf50078b7746bc1c688d14f633ef2","tid":2161173,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:57:26.000Z","msg":"要數近年最受歡迎嘅現役AV女優，現年22歲嘅深田えいみ敢認第一，應該都冇人敢認第二。至於佢咁受歡迎嘅原因，除咗因為樣靚身材正、演出夠上鏡之外，更重要係佢非常識得利用社交網站同Fans互動，但最新一次嘅互動就玩得太大，連佢本人依家都好後悔&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n卻說8月14日時深田えいみ於Twitter上發佈咗一張日清「七味粉杯麵」嘅相，仲話個Post有幾多個Retweet，佢就會落幾多七味粉，結果就引黎日本Twitter網民大規模支持，仲有人好好心咁計埋數，話七味粉中嘅唐辛子食得多其實係會死，致死量就係1kg，而如果以落一下七味粉有0.1g唐辛子黎計，條「死亡線」就係1萬個Retweet。最後只係用咗一日時間，Retweet數已經去到62000個，即係夠死六次&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n但深田えいみ係一個找數真漢子，雖然見到有6萬幾個Retweet已經話「絕望」，但佢依然去超級市場買咗幾大包七味粉，後來更加Post出兩張「七味粉」山，似乎真係試緊點樣先找到數。講真，就算佢最後走數都已經賺哂曝光啦，呢啲咪叫識玩囉！"},{"pid":"3cd2b931eb9ccff695d67a6426e17544eb9dfb66","tid":2161173,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:57:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Eflzl3-UYAEAyGq?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEflzl3-UYAEAyGq%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=9dd0b73c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Eflzl4CUYAAq7zp?format=jpg&amp;name=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEflzl4CUYAAq7zp%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dmedium&h=193455c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Eflzl4HVAAA15HI?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEflzl4HVAAA15HI%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=81185f17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Eflzl4TU8AARqn2?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEflzl4TU8AARqn2%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=